Package: preMetabolizer
Title: A Utility Package for the streamMetabolizer Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Connor", "Brown", , "ConnorBrown1996@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9680-8930"))
Description: Tools for preparing environmental time series before fitting
    stream metabolism models. The package includes helpers for downloading
    meteorological and elevation data, aligning irregular observations,
    converting units, and calculating light, pressure, dissolved gas, and water
    property inputs for streamMetabolizer.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://connorb.github.io/preMetabolizer/, https://github.com/ConnorB/preMetabolizer
